dct_title_s: Reisen in Kleinasien und Nordsyrien. Karte I. C. Humanns's Aufnahmen der Route Brussa - Angora,1882 / [Heinrich Kiepert ] ; C. Ohmann lith.
dct_description_sm: Original map is filed in the Map/Geospatial Center, a map reproduction is attached to companion volume. Relief shown by form lines and spot heights. Ancillary map: Überschit der Ganzen Reise Map shows Karl Humann route, archaelogical sites are located, ancient sites names are given in Greek translation.
